bilingual.source: I want to learn how to print a document.
bilingual.target: 我想学习如何打印文件。

bilingual.source: OK, finally, how do I print my document?
bilingual.target: 好的，最后，我如何打印文档？

bilingual.source: Put some paper in there to print your document.
bilingual.target: 放一些纸进去打印你的文件。

bilingual.source: Print out pictures of your selected works of art.
bilingual.target: 打印出你选择的艺术作品图片。

bilingual.source: We can print Matt's photo on a cardboard cutout.
bilingual.target: 我们可以把马特的照片打印在纸板上。

bilingual.source: Don't forget to check in online and print your boarding pass in advance.
bilingual.target: 别忘了在线值机并提前打印登机牌。

bilingual.source: Use pline to print the text on the screen.
bilingual.target: 使用打印线在屏幕上打印文本。

bilingual.source: Use PrintStream to print the message to the console.
bilingual.target: 使用打印流将消息打印到控制台。

list.abstract: print，英文单词，可用作名词、动词，译为印刷业、印章、打印、出版等。

yingyinNormal.en: George is making blue triangles. Now you print them out. I like doing Mrs. Cat's job.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治画了一些蓝色三角形，现在把它们打印出来。我喜欢猫女士的这份工作。

yingyinNormal.en: George is making blue triangles. Now you print them out. I like doing Mrs. Cat's job.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治画了一些蓝色三角形，现在把它们打印出来。我喜欢猫女士的这份工作。

yingyinNormal.en: It'll get you through that next public speaking gig, pause and print this wellcast worksheet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它会带领你进入公开演讲的圣殿。先暂停，并把wellcast的学习单打印下来。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《公开场合演讲如何展现自信？》

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, I found the court papers that you and Zack need to fill out. I'll print them when we get home. Fine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘿，我找到你和Zack需要签署的法律文件了，我们回家后我就打印出来。好。

yingyinNormal.en: No, here's how love works. You're gonna return the machine, or you can print out a working set of lady parts and sleep with those.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，爱情是这样，要么你退回机器，要么你就打印出一套女性私密部位，跟那"睡"去吧。

yingyinNormal.en: But I've got a plan to find him. How are we going to find Teddy Playgroup, Daddy? First, we print out all the photos we took of him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是我已经想到怎么找它了。我们要怎样才能找到小熊泰迪呢，爸爸？第一步，把拍的所有照片打印出来。

yingyinNormal.en: The end and print. Mummy Pig has finished her works. Ok George, perhaps we can just play one game of Happy Mrs. Chicken. We've earned it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 写完了，然后打印。猪妈妈完成了她的工作。好了乔治，这个时候我们或许可以玩一会快乐小鸡了，因为工作完成了。

yingyinNormal.en: The end and print. Mummy Pig has finished her works. Okay George, perhaps we can just play one game of Happy Mrs Chicken. We've earned it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 写完了，然后打印。猪妈妈完成了她的工作。好了乔治，这个时候我们或许可以玩一会快乐小鸡了，因为工作完成了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, no. But I've got a plan to find him. How are we going to find Teddy Playgroup, Daddy? First, we print out all the photos we took of him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，天呐。但是我已经想到怎么找它了。我们要怎样才能找到小熊泰迪呢，爸爸？第一步，把拍的所有照片打印出来。

yingyinNormal.en: My job is all about drawing shapes on the computer. Then I print the shapes out. And here's another copy. Thank you. What a nice job Mrs. Cat has.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的工作就是在电脑上画各种各样的图形，然后再把这些图形打印出来。我这里还有另外一张。谢谢你，猫女士的工作也很不错。

yingyinNormal.en: My job is all about drawing shapes on the computer. Then I print the shapes out. And here's another copy. Thank you. What a nice job Mrs. Cat has.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的工作就是在电脑上画各种各样的图形，然后再把这些图形打印出来。我这里还有另外一张。谢谢你，猫女士的工作也很不错。

yingyinNormal.en: Mm, butt print. There's no discernible butt print.
yingyinNormal.zh: 坐印，没有明显的坐印。

yingyinNormal.en: And I managed to find this signed print.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而我想办法拿到了这幅有其签名的版本。

yingyinNormal.en: You understand I can use your refusal in print. Yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你明白我可以白纸黑字写明你拒绝回答吧。明白。

yingyinNormal.en: Curse you, fine print!
yingyinNormal.zh: 该死的细则！
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The SpongeBob Movie: Sponge Out of Water》

yingyinNormal.en: The only paper I'm missing now is a big blue print. Is it big and blue?
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在我还需要最后一份文件，一张大大的蓝色的纸。额，一张大大的而且是蓝色的？

yingyinNormal.en: You had a partner? Yeah. When the legend becomes fact, you print the legend.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你曾经还有搭档？是的，当传奇变为现实的时候，你将铭刻传奇。

yingyinNormal.en: But relying instead solely on government policy，to decide how much currency to print.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而是完全凭借政府政策来决定货币发行量。

yingyinNormal.en: But relying instead solely on government policy，to decide how much currency to print.
yingyinNormal.zh: 完全凭借政府政策来决定货币发行量。

yingyinNormal.en: What will you do, then? Nothing, until I have to. Why should a paper print it, anyway?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那您要怎么办？静观其变，到迫不得已时再说，报纸为什么要刊登这种事啊？

word_usage.usage: print既可作及物动词，又可作不及物动词。作及物动词时，其后接名词或代词，如：print the document 打印文件。
print作名词，表示“指纹；手印”时，通常用复数形式，如：His prints were found on the gun. 在枪上发现了他的指纹。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 一楼:亚洲艺术、非洲艺术、美洲印第安艺术、版画和绘画

examination_example.sentence: The scanner examines things such as finger <highlight>prints</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 扫描仪会检查指纹之类的东西。

sense_info_list.en: fix something firmly or indelibly in one's mind

examination_example.sentence: The inventions were clearly <highlight>printed</highlight> on my brain.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些发明清楚地印在我的脑子里。

word_usage.usage:
用作不及物动词时，主动形式含有被动意义。
This picture hasn't printed very well.
这幅画印得不太好。
